            <h2 class="headline">
                <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/06/learning/lesson-plans/border-wall-lesson-plan.html" data-tracking-index="2" data-rref="">Deconstructing the Wall: Teaching About the Symbolism, Politics and Reality of the U.S.-Mexico Border</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="summary">In this lesson plan. students move past the political rhetoric to analyze the function and symbolism of a border wall.</p>
            <p class="byline">
