            <h2 class="headline">
                <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2018/11/07/learning/lesson-plans/is-democracy-at-risk-a-lesson-plan-for-us-and-global-history-classes.html" data-tracking-index="5" data-rref="">Is Democracy at Risk? A Lesson Plan for U.S. and Global History Classes</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="summary">In this lesson, students reflect on why democracies are worth protecting, what elements are essential to a healthy democracy and how it is that democracies sometimes fail.</p>
